    public class InitialModelImpl
extends org.eclipse.emf.internal.cdo.CDOObjectImpl
implements InitialModel
    An implementation of the model object 'Initial Model'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Usage Model
    • Allocation
    • Middleware Repository
    • Event Middle Ware Repository
    • Reconfiguration Rules
    • Monitor Repository
    • Service Level Objectives
    • Repository
    • System
    • Resource Environment
    • Usage Evolution
